# The agent "outbox" is now ONE FILE PER SOURCE under
# data/sources/additional_master_sources/ (<source_id>.csv). Distinct filenames can't
# collide, so parallel recipe PRs never merge-conflict on the outbox — no union driver
# needed. (GitHub's web merge ignores merge=union, which is why the single shared file
# below conflicted on every concurrent PR.) Pin the fragments to LF.
# See data/sources/additional_master_sources/README.md and
# scripts/merge_additional_sources.py.
data/sources/additional_master_sources/*.csv text eol=lf
# The old shared flat file is FROZEN (legacy rows only; new sources go in the folder).
# Keep it LF + union as a belt-and-suspenders in case anything still appends to it.
data/sources/additional_master_sources.csv text eol=lf merge=union
